# Crystallux Financial Services — redirects
# Convenience short URLs. DO NOT add a rule where the source path equals
# the destination's `.html` stem — Cloudflare Pages normalises requests
# by stripping `.html` for matching, which would cause an infinite loop.
# (e.g. /disability → /disability.html would loop because the request
#  /disability.html normalises to /disability and re-fires this rule.)
# Safe rules: source path must differ from destination stem.
/life            /life-insurance.html          301
/ci              /critical-illness.html        301
/travel          /travel-insurance.html        301
/auto            /auto-insurance.html          301
/home-ins        /home-insurance.html          301
/business        /business-insurance.html      301
/quote           /needs-assessment.html        301
/book            /contact.html                 301
/calendly        /contact.html                 301
